### 1. Login
POST http://localhost:3000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "teacher",
  "password": "password123"
}

### 2. Create a Quiz
POST http://localhost:3000/api/quizzes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Math Quiz",
  "description": "A simple math test",
  "teacher_id": 1
}

### 3. Get All Quizzes
GET http://localhost:3000/api/quizzes

### 4. Get a Specific Quiz
GET http://localhost:3000/api/quizzes/1

### 5. Update a Quiz
PUT http://localhost:3000/api/quizzes/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Updated Quiz",
  "description": "Updated description"
}

### 6. Delete a Quiz
DELETE http://localhost:3000/api/quizzes/11